        "faq_shoe": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Is GymGear good for shoe compartment storage?",
            "answer": "<p>GymGear is designed as a compact accessories bag, not a full-size duffel. It does not include a dedicated shoe compartment — it is optimised for essentials like your phone, keys, towel, bottle, and supplements. If you need shoe storage, pair GymGear with your regular gym bag: clip GymGear to the rack for quick-access items, keep your shoes in your main bag. Many UAE gym-goers use this two-bag setup for maximum convenience and hygiene.</p>"
