        "content_1": {
          "type": "content_section",
          "settings": {
            "label": "About This Product",
            "heading": "Magnetic Hands-Free Gym Bag — The Smarter Way to Carry Your Gear",
            "subheading": "",
            "body": "<p>The GymGear <strong>Magnetic Gym Bag</strong> uses <strong>built-in neodymium magnets</strong> with a <strong>magnetic closure</strong> system that snaps onto any stable metal surface — squat racks, cable machines, locker frames, bench supports. Your <strong>sports bag</strong> stays elevated, accessible, and off the dirty gym floor.</p><p>No hooks. No clips. No balancing acts. Just <strong>walk up, snap on, and train hands-free</strong>. When you are done, grab and go in one motion.</p><p><strong>The best gym bag Dubai has to offer.</strong> Whether you train at Fitness First in Dubai Marina, a CrossFit box in JLT, or a hotel gym in Abu Dhabi — this <strong>waterproof gym bag</strong> keeps your phone, keys, wallet, and supplements within arm's reach without touching a single shared surface.</p><p>The <strong>waterproof</strong> nylon fabric handles sweat, rain, and spills. Multiple compartments keep wet gear separate from dry items. Unisex design works for everyone — the ultimate <strong>gym bag Dubai</strong> athletes trust.</p><p><strong>Premium build quality.</strong> Reinforced stitching, heavy-duty zippers, and magnets rated for 5+ kg of hold strength. Compact enough for daily carry, spacious enough for a full gym kit.</p><p>TipTop360 delivers <strong>free next day across all 7 UAE emirates</strong> — Dubai, Abu Dhabi, Sharjah, Ajman, Fujairah, Ras Al Khaimah, and Umm Al Quwain. Cash on Delivery available. 14-day hassle-free returns.</p>",
            "alt_bg": true
          }
        },
        "content_geo_humidity": {
          "type": "content_section",
          "settings": {
            "label": "UAE Climate Ready",
            "heading": "Built for Dubai's Humidity and UAE Weather",
            "subheading": "",
            "body": "<p>UAE gyms generate extreme moisture — from air-conditioned interiors to open-air CrossFit boxes in 45°C heat. The GymGear <strong>waterproof gym bag</strong> is built with waterproof nylon that handles <strong>Dubai humidity</strong>, Abu Dhabi sweat sessions, and Sharjah's coastal air without absorbing odours or breaking down.</p><p>The wet/dry compartment keeps damp towels and sweaty clothes completely separated from your phone, wallet, and clean gear — critical in a climate where condensation and perspiration are constant. Whether you train at Fitness First in Dubai Marina, Gold's Gym in Abu Dhabi, or an outdoor Hyrox circuit in JLT — this <strong>sports bag</strong> is engineered for the UAE environment.</p>",
            "alt_bg": false
          }
        },
        "content_geo_magnets": {
          "type": "content_section",
          "settings": {
            "label": "Magnet Safety",
            "heading": "Are Magnets Safe for Your Phone and Cards?",
            "subheading": "",
            "body": "<p>GymGear uses <strong>shielded neodymium magnets</strong> with a directional magnetic field — the same technology used in MagSafe accessories and laptop closures. The magnets are focused outward toward the metal surface, not inward toward the bag contents.</p><p>Your iPhone, Samsung Galaxy, Apple Watch, AirPods, credit cards, hotel key cards, and Emirates ID are completely safe inside the bag. We have tested this with every major smartphone brand available in the UAE — zero interference, zero data loss, zero demagnetisation. The <strong>magnetic closure</strong> system is designed to hold your bag securely while keeping your electronics protected.</p>",
            "alt_bg": true
          }
        },
        "content_geo_sizing": {
          "type": "content_section",
          "settings": {
            "label": "Sizing Guide",
            "heading": "GymGear Sizing and Capacity Guide",
            "subheading": "",
            "body": "<p>The GymGear <strong>Magnetic Gym Bag</strong> measures 25 cm W × 18 cm H × 10 cm D — compact enough to clip onto any standard gym rack without blocking access, yet spacious enough for a full training session.</p><p><strong>What fits inside:</strong> a standard 500 ml water bottle, phone, keys, towel, wireless earphones, wallet, and small supplements. The 3-zone compartment system separates wet items from dry, and electronics from everything else. Available in Black and Gray — both in a <strong>unisex design</strong> that works for men and women across all ages.</p>",
            "alt_bg": false
          }
        },
        "content_compare": {
          "type": "content_section",
          "settings": {
            "label": "Comparison",
            "heading": "Magnetic vs. Zipper vs. Drawstring — Which Gym Bag Is Best?",
            "subheading": "",
            "body": "<p>Not all gym bags are equal. Here is how the three most common closure types compare for UAE gym-goers:</p><h3>Magnetic Gym Bag (GymGear)</h3><ul><li><strong>Hands-Free Attachment:</strong> Snaps to any metal surface — racks, machines, lockers</li><li><strong>Waterproof:</strong> Yes — waterproof nylon shell built for Dubai humidity</li><li><strong>Wet/Dry Separation:</strong> Built-in 3-zone compartment system</li><li><strong>Hygiene:</strong> Never touches the gym floor</li><li><strong>Phone/Card Safe:</strong> Shielded neodymium magnets protect all electronics</li><li><strong>Best For:</strong> Gym, CrossFit, travel, hotel gyms across the UAE</li></ul><h3>Traditional Zipper Bag</h3><ul><li><strong>Hands-Free:</strong> No — sits on the floor or bench</li><li><strong>Waterproof:</strong> Varies by brand</li><li><strong>Wet/Dry Separation:</strong> Some premium models only</li><li><strong>Hygiene:</strong> Constant floor contact</li><li><strong>Best For:</strong> General use when floor hygiene is not a concern</li></ul><h3>Drawstring Bag</h3><ul><li><strong>Hands-Free:</strong> No — sits on the floor</li><li><strong>Waterproof:</strong> Rarely</li><li><strong>Wet/Dry Separation:</strong> No compartments</li><li><strong>Hygiene:</strong> Constant floor contact, thin fabric absorbs moisture</li><li><strong>Best For:</strong> Light gym sessions, casual use only</li></ul>",
            "alt_bg": true
          }
        },
